# Git commit identity (personal portfolio)

This repo is **personal** — `https://github.com/Aadhavsb/portfolio`.

When committing here, use:

- **Name:** `Aadhav Bharadwaj`
- **Email:** `bharadwajaadhav@gmail.com`

Do **not** use Abeyon email (`aadhav.bharadwaj@abeyon.com`) for this repo.

Before committing, verify:

```bash
git var GIT_AUTHOR_IDENT
git var GIT_COMMITTER_IDENT
```

If either shows Abeyon, override for this commit:

```bash
GIT_AUTHOR_NAME='Aadhav Bharadwaj' \
GIT_AUTHOR_EMAIL='bharadwajaadhav@gmail.com' \
GIT_COMMITTER_NAME='Aadhav Bharadwaj' \
GIT_COMMITTER_EMAIL='bharadwajaadhav@gmail.com' \
git commit ...
```

Remote must stay `origin` → `https://github.com/Aadhavsb/portfolio.git`.
